<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:13:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>意大利消息人士称，中国东风汽车有望在意大利建汽车厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利知情人士周二表示，意大利政府与中国东风汽车集团关于在意大利建设汽车工厂的谈判已进入后期阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:46:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团第二季度表现强劲，因美国反弹超过中国疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</link><description>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团报告称，由于美国的强劲反弹抵消了中国的疲软，第二季度每间可用客房的收入增长了 3.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>舍弗勒第二季度利润下降近30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</link><description>德国机器和汽车零部件制造商舍弗勒公司周二报告称，由于轴承和工业解决方案部门（尤其是欧洲和中国）盈利下滑，第二季度核心利润下降近30%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，全球贸易好转提振中国七月出口扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国7月份的出口可能会以更快的速度攀升，因为制造商受益于全球商品贸易持续好转带来的订单增加，预计这将保持出口强劲并缓解关税恐慌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 05:31:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国公司在等待美国新的限制措施时囤积高端三星芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</link><description>三名消息人士称，华为和百度等中国科技巨头以及初创公司正在囤积三星电子的高带宽内存（HBM）半导体，因为预计美国将限制向中国出口芯片。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 04:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>台股暴跌后反弹 台积电收涨8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</link><description>台湾股市周二收高，摆脱周一创纪录的暴跌，合约芯片制造商台积电上涨 8%，但由于投资者对科技公司和美国经济前景的担忧挥之不去，市场情绪仍保持谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球市场反弹的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</link><description>全球股市周二上涨，部分扭转了前一天的部分大幅跌幅，而在央行官员发表了所有正确的言论来安抚投资者的紧张情绪后，日元稍作喘息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>尽管区域性反弹，中国股市、人民币仍趋于缓和；银行抛售导致收益率上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</link><description>尽管区域性反弹，但中国股市周二跌至六个月低点，人民币兑美元汇率也从周一的七个月高点回落，挑战了中国资产将成为全球市场暴跌的避风港的观点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>日元本月第一天走弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/squeeze-carry-trades-leave-currency-markets-edge-2024-08-06/</link><description>日元周二持稳，瑞士法郎也走软，因为最近几天最引人注目的一些走势有所逆转，市场恢复了一丝平静。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 01:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/squeeze-carry-trades-leave-currency-markets-edge-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在暴跌后寻求缓解反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-05/</link><description>亚洲股市周二有望出现缓解性反弹，因为期货显示遭受重创的日经指数将出现开盘反弹，而且央行官员也发表了所有正确的言论来安抚市场紧张情绪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>百胜中国宣布首席财务官辞职；肯德基、必胜客提振盈利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</link><description>百胜中国周一表示，财务总监杨安迪 (Andy Yeung) 在担任该职位近五年后即将辞职，其季度盈利得益于肯德基和必胜客特许经营店的强劲业绩。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 称法院应拒绝司法部在剥离诉讼中提交的秘密文件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</link><description>TikTok 及其母公司字节跳动周一要求美国上诉法院驳回司法部秘密提起部分法律诉讼的请求，该诉讼捍卫了一项寻求在 1 月 19 日之前强制剥离 TikTok 美国资产或实施禁令的法律。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球股市暴跌的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，全球股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，同时押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>恒大拟向创始人许志安及前高管追回60亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大集团周一表示，其清算人正在寻求向包括创始人许家印在内的七名被告追回约60亿美元，并补充说他们已获得针对其中三人的禁令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手邹敬源卫冕双杠冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，中国选手邹敬源轻松击败对手，卫冕奥运会双杠冠军，获得巴黎奥运会上的第三枚奖牌，为中国队赢得了体操项目的第二枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 10:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>